debian-nvidia-installer (0.14.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Merged upstream changes from devleonardoamaral/debian-nvidia-installer
  * Added support for deb822 sources format (for newer Debian/Ubuntu versions)
  * Added GitHub issue templates (bug reports, documentation, enhancements, questions)
  * Removed forced distro check in requirements
  * Refactored main script with better documentation and structure
  * Improved code organization with documented functions and variables
  * Preserved German translation support in refactored codebase
  * Removed .github/FUNDING.yml

 -- Actionschnitzel <actionschnitzel@guideos.de>  Sun, 08 Dec 2025 12:00:00 +0100

